  "description": "A high-angle, panoramic view captures a sprawling urban and coastal landscape. The foreground is dominated by a dense residential area filled with closely packed houses, predominantly in shades of beige and grey, creating a patchwork effect across the terrain. Beyond the residential area lies a large body of water, likely a bay or estuary, with visible ripples on its surface reflecting the overcast sky. Several bridges span the water, connecting landmasses in the distance. Further in the background, hills and distant landscapes fade into a hazy, grey sky. The overall impression is one of urban expansion meeting the natural environment, with a sense of scale that emphasizes the vastness of the area.",
